courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, B2, C1, C2, C3, C4, C1-C5 elective, D1, and D3. C4 should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). Refer to online catalog for GE course selection and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR). Quarterly advisor meetings are required prior to registration.
